long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e:
Simple and easy way to send links to your ShareDownloader App.

Requirements:
- ShareDownloader Version >= 2.0.0
- Remote server is enabled (In ShareDownloader App)
